      "message": "From rpc/v1/test_result.proto\n\n```\n// A result of a functional test case\nmessage TestResult {\n  \n  // The point in time when the test case started to execute.\n  google.protobuf.Timestamp start_time \u003d 8 \n}\n```\n\n\u003e\u003e start time is optional\nThe message is a result of a test case, which has already happened, and, therefore, the data of start_time must be available in the test_case. Do you mean that TestResult clients don\u0027t have to report the start_time?",
      "parentUuid": "089f374f_34174f13",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 75,
        "startChar": 28,
