      "writtenOn": "2020-01-24T08:35:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "```\n  // When fetch_url expires. If expired, re-request this Artifact.                                       \n  // If fetch_url does not expire, this is unset.                                                        \n  google.protobuf.Timestamp fetch_url_expiration \u003d 3; \n```\n\nIt\u0027s optional. I think it\u0027s valid to put a past timestamp into the fetch_url. It can be done purposely. Also, it doesn\u0027t guarantee that the timestamp is still in future, when this message is handled by TestResult server.",
