      "message": "thinking this a bit more, I am not aware of cases where we will accept it from the users. i.e. the field should be marked with OUTPUT_ONLY (https://aip.dev/203#output-only). Not in this CL. The guideline is that we ignore this field in incoming messages, so we don\u0027t have to validate it.",
